{"tid":1656463,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人民日報: 香港人權與民主法案損人不利己","createTime":"2019-10-15T15:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T16:50:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc7fe3da44072b797773d27d0a9069f0d9514b1","tid":1656463,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/COMMENT-US-191015-22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FCOMMENT-US-191015-22.jpg&h=4635e413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國國會眾議院最快於香港時間周三早上，表決香港人權與民主法案。人民日報網上的評論文章，批評法案損人不利己。<br />\n<br />\n文章以「美國這項法案損人也不利己」為題，批評美國利用法案，粗暴干涉中國內政，不僅不可能奏效，亦將害了自己；又指香港發生的不是和平示威，而美國國會參議員訪港時，在血淋淋的事實面前，竟聲稱沒看到暴力，反問假如發生在美國，他們還會選擇性失明嗎？又指，法案通過後，它保護的不是香港市民，而是暴力份子的人權與民主，又指在中美經貿問題關鍵階段，強推法案無異於開倒車，奉勸美方盡快與香港的暴力割席，不要做暴徒的幫兇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=366394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366394&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLK9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=7fa0b2d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366394&h=5ad8ed7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=366394</a>"},{"pid":"684bf65514a04fcf8c9b2119e61771f1abbfdb58","tid":1656463,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:05:59.000Z","msg":"既然不利美國出咩聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d998659a6b60f824a88c2d291a10e7817825adc4","tid":1656463,"uid":46966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:06:34.000Z","msg":"就算佢地同勇武割席 法案都可以過囉 <img src=\